    "after intra-graph information propagation.",
    "Inter-graph information propagation is then conducted to aggregate information between different graphs.",
    "After the intra-graph information propagation is completed for each graph, any two updated graphs are selected to enable inter-graph word interaction.",
    "The graph attention mechanism is then employed to calculate the final graph representation G f, which is sent to the node attention mechanism to obtain the node representation w f.",
    "Finally, the obtained node representation is fed into a classifier to determine whether the news is fake or real."
